text: Rough Romance is a 1930 American adventure western movie directed by A. F. Erickson and stars George O'Brien, Eddie Borden, Antonio Moreno, Roy Stewart, Harry Cording, John Wayne. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * Category:1930 movies Category:1930s adventure movies Category:1930s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:20th Century Fox movies
